<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚餐的时候，孩子们围坐在餐桌边吃饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比因为和自己的兄弟姐妹再一次在一起吃饭而感到非常开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们怎么知道我在井边的？”他问他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玛莎阿姨担心了。”潘瑟回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们一整天都没看到你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以我们找不到你的时候，我们就决定去森林里看看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊最后说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“够了，简。”潘瑟批评道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简拿了很多炸鸡，她根本吃不了那么多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把这些留给鲍比。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟从简那里把盘子端走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没关系的。简能吃完的。”鲍比微笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家吃惊地地盯着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你今天实在太奇怪了。你还好吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊用关心的语气问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比点点头，认真地问：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们今天都做了什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊打了个哈欠回答说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天真的很奇怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我感觉自己一整天都在睡觉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是。”潘瑟说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我都不记得自己做了什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我什么梦都没做。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她塞了一嘴的炸鸡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玛莎阿姨说她以为我们去基弗先生店里了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她不确定。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等一下。”赛伊怀疑地看着鲍比，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你见过休伊了吗？你许了什么愿望？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是鲍比把一切都告诉了他们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人听了之后都一言不发。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比说完后羞愧地低下了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一直在想，如果我是家里唯一的孩子会是什么样子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我告诉你，那一点儿意思都没有。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比深有感触地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望你现在珍惜像我这么好的哥哥。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊很夸张地张开了他的双臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是他不小心打翻了牛奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛奶全部洒在了简的身上，简大声尖叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“赛伊！”潘瑟用妈妈般的口气说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比笑了，一切都恢复了平常的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，简非常激动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她催着每个人赶快吃完早饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天轮到她许愿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你仔细思考过你的愿望了吗？”潘瑟担心地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然啦！”简不耐烦地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许你应该先告诉我们你要许什么样的愿望。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊建议说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不！”简说着摇摇头，“给你们一个惊喜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他的孩子看了看彼此。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在经历了过去几天的事情之后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们并没有像一开始那么积极去许愿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来吧！”简说着朝大门走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们到井边的时候，鲍比屏住了呼吸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他记得昨天木桶动都不动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，赛伊很轻松地就用绳子顺利地把木桶拉了上来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊的壳就在桶里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们呼唤着休伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了几分钟，休伊终于把他的脑袋探了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在你们开口之前，”他开始说话了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要再一次提醒你们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他伸出了两根手指：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第一，你们许的任何愿望都会在日落时失效。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二，你们许完愿后就不可以再来打扰我了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他盯了鲍比好一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比低头看着自己的脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会让愿望失效，”休伊继续说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以你们在许愿之前必须考虑好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除了简以外的每个人看上去都忧心忡忡的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟和其他人希望简在许愿之前再想一想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但这是我的愿望。”简自己微笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在可以许愿了吗？休伊？”她激动地小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有她按自己想的许愿才公平。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简双手合十，闭上了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>345326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她说：“我希望我们拥有翅膀。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>